    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Designates buildings or groups of buildings that are abandoned by their owners, often constituting potential public hazards. In a legal connotations, the term does not include buildings that are temporarily vacant or unoccupied.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
